    {
      "title": "Schwab Trading Activity Index\u2122: December Score Edges Higher for Third Consecutive Month",
      "url": "https://pressroom.aboutschwab.com/press-releases/press-release/2025/Schwab-Trading-Activity-Index-December-Score-Edges-Higher-for-Third-Consecutive-Month/default.aspx",
      "time_published": "20250106T000000",
      "authors": [],
      "summary": "The Schwab Trading Activity Index\u2122 (STAX) increased to 51.16 in December, marking its third consecutive monthly rise. Schwab clients net bought equities, adding exposure in Health Care and Energy sectors, while selling Information Technology and Communication Services. The report highlights market volatility, key economic data releases, and popular stocks bought and sold by Schwab clients throughout December and the entirety of 2024.",
